we have it backwards, we think “once I get this thing, then I’ll feel happy, whole, abundant, complete” but the feeling never arrives & the chase is always a chase. When you teach your nervous system the feeling in the NOW, not only do you get to experience that emotion you’ve been chasing for so long. The external thing FINALLY comes too. Because you’re not in resistance to it anymore, pushing it away perceiving that you are separate from it. Comment “manifest” and I’ll send you my person guidebook on how I did this and manifested my dream life because of. 🤍 #manifestation #lawofdetachment